      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>This addition to the Hardy Cross Dillard papers was given
         to the library in late 1991 by his widow, Valgerdur Dillard.
         Of interest in the files are congratulatory letters Dillard
         received when he was appointed dean of the University of
         Virginia School of Law. In addition there are numerous awards,
         certificates and degrees Dillard received throughout his life,
         as well as photographs dating from 1911 to 1980.</p>
      </scopecontent>
